  "description": "A sweeping aerial view showcases a sprawling cityscape meeting the expanse of a shimmering bay. The sun breaks through dense, layered clouds, casting dramatic rays of light across the water and illuminating parts of the urban landscape. A long bridge or causeway stretches across the bay, connecting the city to distant landforms. The city itself is a dense grid of buildings, suggesting a large metropolitan area. The foreground features a slightly elevated, darker area with sparse vegetation, providing a sense of perspective and height. The overall scene evokes a sense of vastness and the interplay between natural and man-made elements.",
